  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Save Everhollow before it's too late! Recently, spooky activity of undeniable ghostly nature has been emerging from Shadowthorne Manor — and it's only getting worse each night.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The mayor has turned to you, Alex, a young and fearless ghost hunter, with the mission to investigate the source of this sudden paranormal activity and stop it before it takes over!  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Equipped with the Latest Ghost Tech</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2788740/extras/8dbb1b2a8dd1858bccfb7c5e9d80f6b0.poster.avif?t=1759753869\" width=800 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2788740/extras/8dbb1b2a8dd1858bccfb7c5e9d80f6b0.webm?t=1759753869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2788740/extras/8dbb1b2a8dd1858bccfb7c5e9d80f6b0.mp4?t=1759753869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Capture the unwanted guests with your most trusted Anomalous Multi-Purpose Scanner (A.M.P.S.).  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrade & Outsmart</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2788740/extras/0a46164dcdc061b27833aecda9818f0a.poster.avif?t=1759753869\" width=800 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2788740/extras/0a46164dcdc061b27833aecda9818f0a.webm?t=1759753869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2788740/extras/0a46164dcdc061b27833aecda9818f0a.mp4?t=1759753869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Scavenge the manor for hidden parts to boost your gear, enhance your abilities, and gain the edge over even the most nimble ghosts. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the Dark Secrets of Shadowthorne Manor </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2788740/extras/e27121832734f0e29c331a63b029066f.poster.avif?t=1759753869\" width=800 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2788740/extras/e27121832734f0e29c331a63b029066f.webm?t=1759753869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2788740/extras/e27121832734f0e29c331a63b029066f.mp4?t=1759753869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Shadowthorne Manor is vast, mysterious, and full of surprises. Unlock hidden passageways, uncover long-lost stories, and reveal the secrets lurking in its haunted halls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hunt the emerging ghosts and eliminate the source of the ghost activity</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play the campaign together with a friend</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a manor filled with secrets, history and characters, and find new gear and upgrades to assist you in your ghost hunting task</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >40+ unique and haunted rooms</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A cozy yet eerie adventure for all ages (7+, may vary by country) </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >VR supported</p></li></ul>",
